snippet.title: Dome Romantik Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
If this looks interesting to you, please wishlist on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1637320/Dome_Romantik/
Dome Romantik is coming to Steam and Itch in 2022.

Join our Discord to keep up to date and participate https://discord.gg/AxYpX7AaFP

Choose a dome and mine your way through to the core of the world in this roguelike miner. Hostile lifeforms won't make it easy, but you can install all the right upgrades to deal with any situation.

Music by Cameron Paxton: https://cameronpaxton.bandcamp.com/album/dome-romantik-ost
Made with Godot Engine: https://godotengine.org/
